FCC esengi na ba "patriotes nationalistes" basala liboke na nsima ya Felix Tshisekedi






Alobi azuwi koleka 61%.
O’mokolo ya bosakoli ya ba resultats, bato bayike mpe basala mobulu kasi bakngamaki te.
"Bato ya Félix Tshisekedi basepelaki kasi violence to brutalité ezalaki te. Kasi bamama misusu balongolaki bilamba. Balobi ete basepelaka bongo epyai na bango. Tokangaki bango toyebisaki bango, tokebisaki bango," elobi Gouverneur Muyej.
Koleka 120 balandi misusu ya Fayulu bakangami na etuka ya Haut-Katanga, kolanda sociétécivile.